query: SELECT MAX(P.paperID), COUNT(DISTINCT A.authID) FROM Authors A JOIN Authorship ASH ON A.authID = ASH.authID JOIN Papers P ON ASH.paperID = P.paperID WHERE A.authID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR ASH.authOrder > 66
question: What is the maximum paper ID and the number of distinct authors for authors with IDs between 1 and 10 or authors with author order greater than 66?

query: SELECT instID, country FROM Inst AS i INNER JOIN Authorship AS a ON i.instID = a.instID WHERE a.authOrder = 42
question: What are the institution IDs and countries of institutions with authors who are 42nd in author order?

query: SELECT MIN(paperID), paperID FROM Papers WHERE  paperID != 49
question: What is the paper id that is immediately before 49 in the papers table?

query: SELECT fname FROM Authors JOIN Authorship ON Authorship.authID = Authors.authID WHERE authID < (SELECT AVG(authID) FROM Authorship AS g WHERE  g.paperID = 40) ORDER BY fname ASC
question: What are the first names of authors with an authID less than the average authID of the authors of the paper with paperID 40, listed in ascending order?

query: SELECT paperID FROM Papers WHERE paperID >= 47 ORDER BY paperID DESC LIMIT 1
question: What is the second-highest paper id of papers with ids of 47 or above?

query: SELECT A.lname FROM Authors A INNER JOIN Authorship ASH ON A.authID = ASH.authID INNER JOIN Papers P ON ASH.paperID = P.paperID WHERE P.paperID BETWEEN 1 AND 10
question: What are the last names of the authors of papers with IDs between 1 and 10?

query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.title FROM Papers AS T1 INNER JOIN Authorship AS T2 ON T1.paperID = T2.paperID INNER JOIN Authors AS T3 ON T2.authID = T3.authID WHERE T2.authID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR T2.authID >= 39 LIMIT 6
question: What are the next 6 distinct paper titles authored by authors with IDs between 1 and 10 or 39 and above?

query: SELECT MAX(instID), country FROM Inst WHERE instID > 9 GROUP BY country HAVING AVG(instID) > 95 ORDER BY country ASC
question: For each country, what is the highest institution ID, where the average institution ID is greater than 95, listed in ascending order by country?

query: SELECT AVG(T1.instID) AS avg_instID, T3.lname, T2.title FROM Authorship AS T1 JOIN Papers AS T2 ON T1.paperID = T2.paperID JOIN Authors AS T3 ON T1.authID = T3.authID WHERE T3.fname NOT IN (SELECT fname FROM Authors AS j WHERE  j.authID != 59 LIMIT 7) GROUP BY T3.lname, T2.title
question: What is the average institution ID for authors whose first name is not one of the first 7 unique first names among authors other than the one with author ID 59, grouped by author last name and paper title?

query: SELECT o.paperID FROM Papers AS o WHERE  o.paperID != 53 ORDER BY o.paperID ASC LIMIT 2
question: What are the next two paper IDs, excluding the paper with ID 53, when the papers are ordered by ID in ascending order?

query: SELECT g.instID, g.authID FROM Authorship AS g WHERE g.paperID >= 15 ORDER BY g.instID ASC
question: What are the institution IDs and author IDs for papers with IDs of 15 or more, listed in ascending order by institution ID?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s.paperID), s.authOrder FROM Authorship AS s WHERE s.instID != 93 GROUP BY s.authOrder;
question: How many distinct papers are there for each author count, excluding authors from institution 93?

query: SELECT SUM(T1.paperID), T2.authID FROM Papers AS T1 JOIN Authorship AS T4 ON T1.paperID = T4.paperID JOIN Authors AS T2 ON T2.authID = T4.authID JOIN Inst AS T3 ON T3.instID = T4.instID WHERE T4.authID BETWEEN 1 AND 10
question: What is the sum of paper IDs for each author with an author ID between 1 and 10?

query: SELECT paperID FROM Papers WHERE paperID > (SELECT MAX(paperID) FROM Authorship)
question: What are the paper IDs that are greater than the maximum paper ID of any authorship?

query: SELECT Authorship.instID, fname, country FROM Inst JOIN Authors JOIN Papers JOIN Authorship ON Authorship.paperID = Papers.paperID AND Authorship.authID = Authors.authID AND Inst.instID = Authorship.instID WHERE  Authorship.paperID = 5 GROUP BY country HAVING MAX(authOrder) > 3 ORDER BY Authorship.instID DESC LIMIT 8
question: What are the institution ids, first names, and countries of authors for paper with id 5, where the maximum author order is more than 3, listed in descending order of institution ids, from the 9th to the 16th result?

query: SELECT fname, lname FROM Authors WHERE lname != (SELECT lname FROM Authors ORDER BY lname DESC LIMIT 1) LIMIT 4;
question: What are the first and last names of the first four authors who are not the one with the last name that comes last in alphabetical order?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n.lname), n.fname, n.lname FROM Authors AS n GROUP BY n.fname, n.lname HAVING AVG(n.authID) < 61 LIMIT 9
question: What are the names of the 10th to 18th authors who on average have published a paper with an id less than 61?

query: SELECT title FROM Papers WHERE paperID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR paperID > 85 GROUP BY title HAVING MAX(paperID) = 76 ORDER BY title DESC LIMIT 5
question: What are the titles of papers from the last 5 groups, whose paper IDs are either between 1 and 10 or greater than 85, where the maximum paper ID within each group is 76, listed in descending order?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT fname), COUNT(DISTINCT Authors.authID), COUNT(DISTINCT Authorship.authID) FROM Authors JOIN Authorship ON Authorship.authID = Authors.authID WHERE  authOrder > 63 LIMIT 1
question: How many unique first names, author IDs in the Authors table and Authorship table are there for the authors with an author order greater than 63?

query: SELECT MIN(instID) AS min_instID, country FROM Inst WHERE instID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR instID = 28 GROUP BY country ORDER BY MIN(instID) DESC
question: What is the country and the smallest institution ID in each country for institutions with IDs between 1 and 10 or exactly 28, listed in descending order of the smallest institution ID?

query: SELECT c.title, COUNT(c.paperID) AS paper_count, COUNT(DISTINCT c.paperID) AS distinct_paper_count FROM Papers AS c WHERE c.paperID >= 40 OR c.paperID IN (SELECT paperID FROM Papers WHERE paperID >= 27) GROUP BY c.title ORDER BY c.title DESC LIMIT 9
question: What are the titles of the 10th to 18th papers in descending order, along with their total and distinct paper counts, for papers with an ID of 40 or higher or those that also have an ID of 27 or higher?

query: SELECT I.name FROM Authors AS A JOIN Authorship AS Au ON A.authID = Au.authID JOIN Papers AS P ON Au.paperID = P.paperID JOIN Inst AS I ON Au.instID = I.instID WHERE Au.paperID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Au.instID < 97 ORDER BY I.name ASC;
question: What are the names of the institutions with authors who have published papers with IDs between 1 and 10, and the institution IDs are less than 97, listed in ascending order?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.paperID), T2.lname FROM Authorship AS T1 JOIN Authors AS T2 ON T1.authID = T2.authID JOIN Inst AS T3 ON T3.instID = T1.instID WHERE T2.fname IN ( SELECT fname FROM Authors AS p WHERE p.authID <= 83 LIMIT 2 ) LIMIT 1
question: What is the count of distinct papers and the last name of the author when considering authors with first names matching the first two authors with an author id less than or equal to 83, excluding the first result?

query: SELECT Papers.paperID, title FROM Papers JOIN Authorship ON Authorship.paperID = Papers.paperID WHERE Authorship.instID > 67 ORDER BY Papers.paperID DESC
question: What are the paper IDs and titles of papers with authors from institutions with an ID greater than 67, listed in descending order by paper ID?

query: SELECT MIN(p.paperID), AVG(p.paperID), p.title FROM Papers AS p JOIN Papers ON Papers.paperID = p.paperID WHERE p.paperID IN (SELECT paperID FROM Authorship WHERE instID = 21) GROUP BY p.title
question: What are the minimum and average paper IDs for each paper title of papers published by authors from institution 21?

query: SELECT Inst.instID, Authorship.instID, Authors.authID FROM Inst JOIN Authors JOIN Papers JOIN Authorship ON Authorship.paperID = Papers.paperID AND Authorship.authID = Authors.authID AND Inst.instID = Authorship.instID WHERE  Authorship.instID != 86
question: What are the institution IDs, author IDs, and institution IDs of authors from institutions other than institution 86?

query: SELECT MAX(Authorship.instID), Inst.country FROM Authorship JOIN Authors ON Authorship.authID = Authors.authID JOIN Inst ON Inst.instID = Authorship.instID WHERE Authorship.authID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Authors.authID < 54 LIMIT 6
question: What are the institution ids and countries of the top 6 institutions (starting from the 7th) where authors with ids between 1 and 10 or less than 54 have published papers, ordered by the maximum institution id?

query: SELECT MIN(paperID) FROM Papers WHERE paperID != 52
question: What is the smallest paper ID other than 52?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.paperID), a.paperID, p.title FROM Authorship AS a JOIN Papers AS p ON a.paperID = p.paperID WHERE a.paperID >= 69 GROUP BY p.title;
question: What are the distinct paper IDs and their counts for papers with IDs 69 and above, grouped by paper title?

query: SELECT MIN(f.paperID) FROM Papers AS f WHERE f.paperID < 87;
question: What is the smallest paper id less than 87?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.authID), T1.instID FROM (SELECT DISTINCT Authors.authID, Authorship.instID FROM Authors JOIN Authorship ON Authorship.authID = Authors.authID WHERE Authorship.instID = 36) AS T1
question: How many distinct authors are from institution 36, and what is their institution id?
